ActCanadian Air Transport Security Authority Act
PrecisAppointment of PETER CARDON WALLIS of Calgary, Alberta, to be a director of the board of directors of the Canadian Air Transport Security Authority, to hold office during pleasure for a term of three years, in the place of M.H. (Mike) Shaikh.
